    # (blank line)
    ""Miles away, in her silent, grass-floored shuttle, FoF leans forward in her chair, utterly captivated. GrahamCracker, her ginger kitten, purrs on a nearby console, batting playfully at a holographic projection of a complex social diagram. The data streaming from the drone is a firehose of sensory input. Through BailieBoy’s senses, she experiences the scene with startling fidelity: the sharp, acrid scent of human sweat, the low whine of canine anxiety, the slap of bare feet on tatami mats.""
