    ""BailieBoy is chasing a discarded food wrapper that’s tumbling in the wind. You’re barely paying attention. Your mind is a whirlwind of Zorya, Kaito, and the impossible choice you’re facing. Your mother’s face appears in your vision, and you force a smile.""
