    ""***An Audit of Reality***""
    # (blank line)
    ""High on the thrill of your new life and your own burgeoning heroism, you meet Jay for a sparring session a few days later. You’re faster this time, your blocks are cleaner, and you even manage to land a light, glancing blow to his shoulder.""
    # (blank line)
