    ""You let out a breath you didn’t realize you were holding. It’s over. You’ve done it. You’ve reached into the machine and edited reality. A surge of power, intoxicating and absolute, washes over you. You are more than a janitor. You are a god.""
    # (blank line)
    ""Zorya’s lips are on your neck. “Thank you,” she whispers. Her kiss is deep, passionate, a reward and a promise. As she leads you away from the terminal towards your bed, you don’t see the final, silent message that Gemini flashes in your neural lace before archiving it.""
